THE SECRET ADVENTURES OF JULES VERNE
The steam-punk adventures of the young Jules Verne and his fellow travelers aboard the airship Aurora

18. THE INQUISITOR  11/18/2000 

When a college friend of Rebecca&#039;s, Amateratsu, and her grandfather Kajimori travel to Paris from Japan, the grandfather is kidnapped by the Inquisitor, a member of the League of Darkness. Kajimori has knowledge of a potion of "enlightenment," which he has passed on to Amateratsu.
